Yes
you don't have to pay.
Well that would have solved a lot of problems last night, lol

Mark of a good LGS: The local store is closed on Sunday at six, so sometimes a friend of mine hosts games at his place on Sunday nights, and I decided to play last night. I showed up at 6, and found out his AC had crapped out during the day so it was sweltering even in his basement. He sent out a message to the Facebook group that we were gonna cancel since it's too hot to play at this place, and the guy who owns the local store who is also in the group messaged back immediately that if we wanted to play he'd keep the shop open. So we all headed over there, and by the time we arrived another half a dozen people from the group had shown up.
Shop owner had ordered pizza too.
